contentrichtext.text: {{italictitle}} {{Taxobox | name = ''Xymene gouldi'' | image = | image_caption = | status = | regnum = [[Animal]]ia | phylum = [[Mollusc]]a | classis = [[Gastropoda]] | unranked_superfamilia = clade [[Caenogastropoda]]<br/>clade [[Hypsogastropoda]]<br/>clade [[Neogastropoda]] | superfamilia = [[Muricoidea]] | familia = [[Muricidae]] | subfamilia = [[Trophoninae]] | genus = ''[[Xymene]]'' | species = '''''X. gouldi''''' | binomial = ''Xymene gouldi'' | binomial_authority = (Cossmann, 1903) | synonyms = ''Trophon crispus'' <small>[[Frederick Wollaston Hutton|Hutton]], 1886</small><br>''Trophon gouldi'' <small>Cossmann, 1903</small> }} '''''Xymene gouldi''''' is a [[species]] of [[predatory]] sea [[snail]], a [[marine (ocean)|marine]] [[gastropod]] [[mollusc]] in the [[family (biology)|family]] [[Muricidae]], the rock snails or murex snails. ==References== {{reflist}} * [[Arthur William Baden Powell|Powell A W B]], ''New Zealand Mollusca'', [[HarperCollins|William Collins Publishers Ltd]], Auckland, New Zealand 1979 ISBN 0-00-216906-1 {{DEFAULTSORT:Xymene Gouldi}} [[Category:Muricidae]] {{Muricidae-stub}}
